Server Port Configuration:
	Edit /etc/services and add "ez-ntp		50000/tcp"

Building & Installing:
	1. Modify the make files to fit your system(s)
	2. make
	3. sudo make install
	4. Copy the startup files (*.sh) into the appropriate directories
	   Debian: /etc/init.d (also run update-rc.d)
	   FreeBSD: /usr/local/etc/rc.d
